# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BabyBloom environment variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in real values.
# .env.local is gitignored — never commit real credentials.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google OAuth Client ID for Google Drive sync (zero-knowledge encrypted backup)
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
#   2. Create/select a project
#   3. APIs & Services → Library → enable "Google Drive API"
#   4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#   5. Application type: Web application
#   6. Authorized redirect URIs:
#        http://localhost:5173/oauth    ← local dev (Vite default port)
#        https://yourdomain.com/oauth   ← production
#   7. For native (Capacitor) builds also add:  babybloom://oauth
#
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
